title: Turbo Jam Disk 1
description:
Turbo Jam does not require special equipment no heavy bags or shields just an emphasis on form, technique, and fun. The basic moves are simple and can be done by anyone at almost any fitness level, though as the workouts advance, they become more exciting and powerful. But mostly, it&#039;s the high-spirited party atmosphere of Turbo Jam that makes it different from other exercise programs. Its addictive, up-tempo dance beats quickly made it the hottest group-exercise kickboxing program in the country.
